From dci@math.uchicago.edu Fri Feb  3 09:24:50 1995
Received: from ford.uchicago.edu (ford.uchicago.edu [128.135.72.47]) by pasteur.EECS.Berkeley.EDU (8.6.9/8.6.4) with ESMTP id OAA03402 for <gmeeker@sharrock.EECS.Berkeley.EDU>; Thu, 2 Feb 1995 14:02:49 -0800
Received: (dci@localhost) by ford.uchicago.edu (8.6.9/8.6.5) id QAA22338 for gmeeker@sharrock.EECS.Berkeley.EDU; Thu, 2 Feb 1995 16:02:37 -0600
From: Dan Isaksen <dci@math.uchicago.edu>
Message-Id: <199502022202.QAA22338@ford.uchicago.edu>
Subject: Re: New CalChart
To: gmeeker@sharrock.EECS.Berkeley.EDU (Garrick Meeker)
Date: Thu, 2 Feb 1995 16:02:36 -0600 (CST)
In-Reply-To: <Pine.HPP.3.91.950201174049.2363A-100000@sharrock.EECS.Berkeley.EDU> from "Garrick Meeker" at Feb 1, 95 06:26:02 pm
X-Mailer: ELM [version 2.4 PL13]
Content-Type: text
