reasonable?  The user could use the arrow keys together with the keyboard
commands to do just about anything, albeit slowly and painfully.

Keyboard browsing the menus and icon lists can be ditched without much loss of
functionality.  Remember that I've got the "kitchen sink" attitude in
writing this outline.  Anything that has the slightest chance of being
included should be discussed first.
 
