animation subroutine.  I was thinking that the parser should check for
proper grammar as soon as you exit the text editor, rather than waiting
until you try to animate.  Should we allow basic cut/paste actions?

How about an auto-animate?  You press a button, and the show moves through
all of the animation at a prespecified rate.  Prevents your finger from
getting tired clicking the mouse so much.

