Then I copied the files into the proper subdirectories:

gcc -fpcc-struct-return -o calchart -O2      -L/usr/X11R6/lib common/main.o common/gui.o common/disk.o  common/config.o xlib/stub.o xlib/images.o  show.o loadshow.o prntshow.o  -lXext -lX11      
